text: Input/Output Data The agent emits and retrieves UDRs of any defined type. MIM The agent does not publish or access any additional MIM parameters. However, MIM parameters can be published through agent configuration, see the MIM Tab section in Python Collection Agent Configuration - Batch . For further information about available functions, see Functions for Python .
